{"tid":34632,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)千與千尋","createTime":"2016-12-11T14:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T16:35:18.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0686235d48d85c5c63acfde4cd348437e0ad0a5d","tid":34632,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:49:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour&d=5HBBM7S7erSiSLv4VqhfqnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=d27c4a20\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour</a>暫時用住SKLIVE睇先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/61/Spirited_away.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F61%2FSpirited_away.jpg&h=92800862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n年僅10歲的荻野千尋是一個普通的四年級小學生，她正隨著父母搬家來到一個陌生的城鎮準備開始一個全新生活。後續因途中迷路，千尋和父母誤闖入了一個人類不應該進入的靈異小鎮。而小鎮裡存有著一棟給予讓各方眾神泡澡歇憩、名為「油屋」的澡堂，該澡堂則是被一名稱做「湯婆婆」的魔女所持有。<br />\n<br />\n之後在小鎮裡千尋的父母由於一時貪吃；於未經允許情況下隨意享用一間餐館裡的食物，而遭到湯婆婆的懲罰將兩人變成了豬..<br />\n<br />\n11 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa74473a068aeca4e80463ec9799491e5d4c98c","tid":34632,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e6a6b1576be437f13e70750339a054accfa12b","tid":34632,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0c53978d91a9289ddc34810f4fb396178944fa","tid":34632,"uid":29160,"like":0,"d